Ayo duduk di sini. Tolong bersihkan meja ini!

00:22:38.190 --> 00:22:39.441
Apa ini, pemakaman?

00:22:39.984 --> 00:22:40.985
Hai.

00:22:41.068 --> 00:22:42.987
Munjeong belum ada di sini.

00:22:43.070 --> 00:22:45.447
Kalau kita makan duluan,
kita akan dimarahi lagi.

00:22:45.531 --> 00:22:46.574
Astaga.

